      <title>欧盟拟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/eu-moves-toward-hitting-china-with-tariffs-on-electric-vehicles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟即将对进入欧盟的中国电动汽车征收额外关税，理由是新的证据表明北京政府正在为该行业提供非法金融支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/eu-moves-toward-hitting-china-with-tariffs-on-electric-vehicles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其在美国和俄罗斯之间的外交难题中走钢丝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/turkey-walks-tightrope-between-us-and-russia-in-diplomacy-puzzle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其在保持与俄罗斯关系的同时，也在努力改善与美国的军事关系，部分方式是开始遵守对莫斯科的金融制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/turkey-walks-tightrope-between-us-and-russia-in-diplomacy-puzzle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:06:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将在带薪育儿假期间支付养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/australia-will-pay-pension-contributions-on-paid-parental-leave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚政府将做出期待已久的改革，为休带薪育儿假的工人支付养老金，这是中左翼工党政府解决该国劳动力性别不平等问题的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/australia-will-pay-pension-contributions-on-paid-parental-leave</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜利为里根共和党写墓志铭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-s-triumph-writes-an-epitaph-for-reagan-republican-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，唐纳德·特朗普在初选中大获全胜，消除了人们一直以来的疑虑，即长期以来效忠罗纳德·里根世界观的共和党已经转变为一个由特朗普主导的政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-s-triumph-writes-an-epitaph-for-reagan-republican-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
