    <item>
      <title>埃及大幅加息后货币贬值超过35%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-unexpectedly-hikes-interest-rate-to-27-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及提高了利率，并允许其货币贬值超过35%，这是期待已久的贬值，这可能为国际货币基金组织增加数十亿美元的贷款铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-unexpectedly-hikes-interest-rate-to-27-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国捍卫5%的增长目标，暗示流动性增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/china-defends-5-target-vows-vigorous-effort-to-grow-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高经济官员为今年经济增长约 5% 的计划进行了辩护，并暗示可能会增加流动性。一天前，一些经济学家因认为缺乏足够的政策支持而对这一雄心勃勃的目标表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/china-defends-5-target-vows-vigorous-effort-to-grow-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
